16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 75 O.S. 2021, Section 308, as
17 amended by Section 5, Chapter 38, O.S.L. 2023 (75 O.S. Supp. 2024,
18 Section 308), is amended to read as follows:
19 Section 308. A. Upon receipt of any proposed permanent rules,
20 the Speaker of the House of Representatives and the President Pro
21 Tempore of the Senate shall assign such rules to the appropriate
22 committees of each house of the Legislature for review. Except as
23 otherwise provided by this section:
